that the information is

00:40:33.730 --> 00:40:37.060
used to gain a thermodynamic
advantage to convert heat

00:40:37.060 --> 00:40:39.313
into work, but in
a small amount,

00:40:39.313 --> 00:40:41.230
and that if you go on
doing that cumulatively,

00:40:41.230 --> 00:40:43.572
sooner or later,
you have to erase

00:40:43.572 --> 00:40:45.280
the information in
the register, and then

00:40:45.280 --> 00:40:49.690
