gain that you've had.

00:40:52.010 --> 00:40:55.210
So it's not a free lunch,
but if the name of the game

00:40:55.210 --> 00:40:58.900
is to play the margins of
thermodynamics on a nano scale,

00:40:58.900 --> 00:41:00.660
then that's certainly
what life is doing.

00:41:00.660 --> 00:41:02.190
But I didn't have time.

00:41:02.190 --> 00:41:04.510
Life is doing much
more than just

00:41:04.510 --> 00:41:06.610
playing a thermodynamic game.

00:41:06.610 --> 00:41:09.490
It's also doing this
complex organization,

00:41:09.490 --> 00:41:11.590
encoded information
management, and so on.

00:41:11.590 --> 00:41:14.530
And all of that has to come
in any true understanding

00:41:14.530 --> 00:41:15.490
of the nature of life.

00:41:15.490 --> 00:41:18.730
And so the game of
chess I skipped over

00:41:18.730 --> 00:41:21.910
would have been, if I'd have had
time and attempt to explain how

00:41:21.910 --> 00:41:24.490
I think we can
capture that concept

00:41:24.490 --> 00:41:28.330
of functional or meaningful
information in a context,

00:41:28.330 --> 00:41:31.870
in a new type of physical law,
which was what Schrodinger

00:41:31.870 --> 00:41:32.550
was suggesting.

00:41:32.550 --> 00:41:35.880
It would be a sort of top
down law, in which the-- just

00:41:35.880 --> 00:41:40.120
to give you the words, in
which the dynamical update

00:41:40.120 --> 00:41:44.080
rules, if you like the
evolution of the system,

00:41:44.080 --> 00:41:46.138
will be a function of
the state of the system,

00:41:46.138 --> 00:41:47.680
quite unlike any
law of physics we've

00:41:47.680 --> 00:41:49.420
had so far, where
the laws are fixed,

00:41:49.420 --> 00:41:51.200
the states change with time.

00:41:51.200 --> 00:41:55.040
We're advocating that the laws
are a function of the state,

00:41:55.040 --> 00:41:57.520
and that gives whole new
pathways to complexity.

00:41:57.520 --> 00:42:02.420
And we've done some computer
models to bolster that claim.

00:42:02.420 --> 00:42:05.320
So that's why I think the new
type of physical law comes in,

00:42:05.320 --> 00:42:08.140
but this is still
a work in progress.

00:42:08.140 --> 00:42:11.813
AUDIENCE: Do you think physics
