really three great origin

00:42:31.930 --> 00:42:34.790
problems-- the universe, the
life, and then consciousness.

00:42:34.790 --> 00:42:36.790
I think we've cracked the
problem, more or less,

00:42:36.790 --> 00:42:38.040
