00:43:05.530 --> 00:43:08.180
network of researchers,
who like these things.

00:43:08.180 --> 00:43:12.240
And one of these
is Giulio Tunoni.

00:43:12.240 --> 00:43:15.340
He's a neuroscientist, and
he's defined something called

00:43:15.340 --> 00:43:17.110
