00:43:28.510 --> 00:43:30.880
that the collective
system has greater

00:43:30.880 --> 00:43:32.740
power than the components.

00:43:32.740 --> 00:43:35.500
And he can demonstrate that
for certain types of networks

00:43:35.500 --> 00:43:37.460
with certain types
of feedback loops.

00:43:37.460 --> 00:43:39.760
So in principle, if you
