00:46:22.902 --> 00:46:23.610
PAUL DAVIES: Yes.

00:46:23.610 --> 00:46:25.027
AUDIENCE: --In the
direction, then

00:46:25.027 --> 00:46:29.030
lets every molecule approaching
it at a faster speed than that

00:46:29.030 --> 00:46:29.560
through.

00:46:29.560 --> 00:46:31.140
