00:46:32.753 --> 00:46:34.170
PAUL DAVIES: Ah,
no, but the demon

00:46:34.170 --> 00:46:38.040
has to be able to
observe and assess

00:46:38.040 --> 00:46:40.630
the speeds of those molecules.

00:46:40.630 --> 00:46:43.420
And then is this one
coming fast enough?

00:46:43.420 --> 00:46:45.290
And then yes, open the shutter.

00:46:45.290 --> 00:46:50.310
You see, so the person who
