00:46:55.530 --> 00:47:00.900
and had a single molecule in
a box with a movable screen.

00:47:00.900 --> 00:47:02.310
It's called Szilard's Engine.

00:47:02.310 --> 00:47:04.590
It's much discussed in my book.

00:47:04.590 --> 00:47:09.272
