and extract the work.

00:47:13.590 --> 00:47:15.620
But then in order to
repeat that cycle,

00:47:15.620 --> 00:47:19.200
it would have to eliminate the
information from its register

00:47:19.200 --> 00:47:20.220
or accumulate it.

00:47:20.220 --> 00:47:23.820
And then if it accumulates,
if it's a finite register,

00:47:23.820 --> 00:47:27.400
then eventually all this
